      "message": "Why don\u0027t we promote some more clamps to skvm::Builder?\n\n   skvm::F32 clamp  (skvm::F32 x, skvm::F32 lo, skvm::F32 hi);\n   skvm::F32 clamp0_(skvm::F32 x, skvm::F32 hi)                { return clamp(x, splat(0.0f),         hi); }\n   skvm::F32 clamp01(skvm::F32 x)                              { return clamp(x, splat(0.0f), splat(1.0f); }\n\nNot exactly sure what the best name for clamp0_ is... we could just name them all clamp() even.  Might be clamp01() brings all the benefit anyway.\n\n(I\u0027m happy to do the backfill as a follow up.)",
